{"tid":2055750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許智峯入稟民事禁制大陸製有毒催淚彈明天開庭","createTime":"2020-06-08T07:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T10:28:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e56a5addad6461cabfb24c905148da8d7cad2e6b","tid":2055750,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/huichifung913/photos/a.402989486549920/1523466581168866/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhuichifung913%2Fphotos%2Fa.402989486549920%2F1523466581168866%2F&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=c9fbdf78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/huichifung913/photos/a.402989486549920/1523466581168866/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/103304944_1523466584502199_6406526152681504367_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=6baczD-YhocAX8f3qa8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=67d3aee6dbead5879f84db15e725e09e&amp;oe=5F03307F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F103304944_1523466584502199_6406526152681504367_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D6baczD-YhocAX8f3qa8%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D67d3aee6dbead5879f84db15e725e09e%26oe%3D5F03307F&h=7ed1c54b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方在過去一年多次使用催淚化學武器「放題」，不斷殘害市民，卻一直拒絕公開當中的化學成份。民主黨立法會議員許智峯早前從民事入稟，要求警方公佈催淚彈所含的化學成份，法庭聆訊將在明天上午10時半於高等法院開庭！<br />\n<br />\n許智峯坦言，催淚彈的化學成份對市民，特別是孕婦、小孩、老人影響極深，他們一旦吸引有害化學品，會嚴重影響健康甚至有生命危險。自反送中運動以來，警暴問題無日無之，警員濫捕、無制約使用武力，情況失控：警察開真槍射市民、交通警電單車故意撞人、住宅區TG放題，香港人面對這些毫無法理、無法無天的警員，既憤怒亦難過。失職、濫捕的警察必須為個人失控、非法的行為負上責任，他們必定自食其果。"},{"pid":"2e11fd1bf67fc0635605fbe5f28fbbfc7086932b","tid":2055750,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif